        <item>General</item>
        <item>Why does watermarking take so long?</item>
        <item>Why is there a \'temp\' video?</item>
        <item>How can I change the video quality?</item>
        <item>Can I disable the preview?</item>
        <item>How do I embed my location in the watermark?</item>
